OL,3,CAdventurer becomes first disabled
OL,4,Cperson to ski solo to South Pole
OL,6,FA former GB Para-athlete has made
OL,7,Fhistory after becoming the first
OL,8,Fdisabled person to ski solo and
OL,9,Funsupported to the South Pole.
OL,11,FJonny Huntington, from Kingsbridge in
OL,12,Fsouth Devon, covered 566 miles of
OL,13,FAntarctic tundra in 46 days despite
OL,14,Fthe effects of the debilitating stroke
OL,15,Fhe suffered in 2014.
OL,17,FThe 38-year-old set off from Fuchs-
OL,18,FMessner on the edge of the Antarctic
OL,19,Flandmass on November 21 2024 and
OL,20,Farrived at the South Pole on Monday 6
OL,21,FJanuary.
