OL,6,FThroughout his expedition, he skied in
OL,7,Fextreme conditions including freezing
OL,8,Ftemperatures and 24-hour sunlight,
OL,9,Fwhile dragging an 110kg sled carrying
OL,10,Fhis food and equipment.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country on
OL,13,FThursday 9 January, he said: "It's
OL,14,Fstill sinking in if I'm honest. I
OL,15,Fthink it'll probably take me weeks, if
OL,16,Fnot months, to properly process what's
OL,17,Fjust sort of taking place over the
OL,18,Flast couple of months for me.
