OL,6,F"I'm actually feeling great. I've been
OL,7,Foff the ice for 72 hours now and the
OL,8,Frecovery actually has been quite
OL,9,Fremarkable.
OL,11,F"I wouldn't necessarily say I was up
OL,12,Ffor doing the whole thing over again
OL,13,Fright now, but I'm certainly in high
OL,14,Fspirits and feeling physically great."
OL,16,FJonny said his support team, which
OL,17,Fincluded his sister, were keeping him
OL,18,Fmotivated with messages from home.
