OL,6,FIn terms of the weather, he said:
OL,7,F"It's incredibly sunny here at the
OL,8,Fminute - there's not a cloud in the
OL,9,Fsky, and it's actually been very, very
OL,10,Fwarm for Antarctica at this time of
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,F"The inside of my tent was getting up
OL,14,Fto plus 25 degrees because of the
OL,15,Fsunlight, and that meant the snow was
OL,16,Fvery, very soft.
