OL,6,F"So with a heavy sledge laden behind
OL,7,Fyou, the sheer physicality of the task
OL,8,Fwas by far the most challenging thing
OL,9,FI've ever done. It was physically
OL,10,Fexhausting every day."
OL,12,FJonny said he's tried to maintain a
OL,13,Fpositive mindset throughout the
OL,14,Fpreparation process.
