OL,6,FHe said: "I'm not trying to convert
OL,7,Fother people into polar explorers, but
OL,8,Fat the same time, what I am trying to
OL,9,Fdo is really encourage people
OL,10,Fregardless of the position or
OL,11,Fdisadvantage they find themselves in,
OL,12,Fto set themselves big goals."
OL,14,FOnly 52 people have successfully skied
OL,15,Fto the South Pole without support but
OL,16,FMr Huntington is understood to be the
OL,17,Ffirst explorer with a disability to do
OL,18,Fso.
