OL,6,FThe former Army officer was left
OL,7,Fparalysed from the neck down on his
OL,8,Fleft side when he suffered his stroke
OL,9,Fat the age of 28.
OL,11,FIt took years of rehabilitation before
OL,12,Fhe was able to fully walk again, and
OL,13,Feven then he was left with restricted
OL,14,Fmovement down his left side.
OL,16,FHe said the final stage of his
OL,17,Fexpedition was much more challenging
OL,18,Fbecause he encountered huge ice
OL,19,Fformations called sastrugi and soft
OL,20,Fsnow, which made progress difficult.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
