OL,6,FHe also had a lot more climbing to do
OL,7,Fwhile skiing for nine to 11 hours and
OL,8,Fcovering between 11 and 14 miles per
OL,9,Fday.
OL,11,FDuring his stroke recovery, Mr
OL,12,FHuntington became a member of the
OL,13,FArmed Forces Para-Snowsport Team,
OL,14,Fwhich ignited his love for skiing.
OL,16,FHe went on to join the GB Para Nordic
OL,17,Fski team, competing between 2017 and
OL,18,F2020 at World Cups all over the world.
