OL,6,FThe idea for his South Pole expedition
OL,7,Fcame after he stopped skiing
OL,8,Fcompetitively.
OL,10,FMr Huntington, who had been planning
OL,11,Fand training for the expedition for
OL,12,Ffive years, said he felt very
OL,13,Femotional when he reached the
OL,14,FCeremonial South Pole.
